Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不生气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.40,0:00:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有生气的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.76,0:00:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于肯说话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在想要等到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不怎么喝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啤酒可以的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服借一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快点换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直闷在房间里好几天没洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是会介意这个的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长在录音室等你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝一罐啤酒又不用多少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得冬弥君…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在车上喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.31,0:03:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥君？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我昨天…做了那样的事  以为音乐节的事已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样就不行的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只能说明这就是此等程度的闹剧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来干杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝贺我们避免了时间的浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这是由绮的第一次的反抗  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这个进步  我想坦率地高兴一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到想给奖励的程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.49,0:04:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么理奈不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加愚蠢的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈是我的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮是除此以外的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来  由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你介绍下你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是绝对的秘密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那一天  从那一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集画成为了目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拜托长濑帮我收集的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了很多人力  时间和金钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  看上去每幅画都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而没有一幅是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是赝品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在伦敦看到的不是这些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是在这一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在寻找着那仅此一幅的画
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈她没有能成为真品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮  现在的你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些画都不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来由绮有看画的眼光…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说这只是视力的问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确这些并不是完全一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是人类画的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然对画不怎么了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这些画里的人都不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么  由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方先生才是  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戏弄我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说点什么吧  弗兰奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你是经纪人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演员开这么差劲的玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早知道了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  弗兰奇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此  还拿别的画来欺骗我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去  由绮你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不该…说出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮小姐  国王可能是赤裸着身体的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把工作当什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是毫无办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔会觉得理奈是个房间里的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆当成是幅画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小英居然有这样的嗜好  真是意外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪里知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一幅画想让你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是鉴赏家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:09:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个女孩呢  还有百合花来着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花开得很大的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.26,0:09:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作者叫杰弗里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认识作者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年后想再见一次  而画却不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未忘记…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这幅画
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  想要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意让给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不能免费
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你开价吧  要多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  来场游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候已经…我的命运已尽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要成为我的伙伴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  你看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以少女为主题的印象画展
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  来这边把衣服脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是不是依靠感官的外行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是听从我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我命令的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你趴在地下舔我鞋子也行  没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么快点脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像狗一样趴在这里舔我的脚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都听我的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  给你写一曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不满吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来嘲笑我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让还什么都不懂的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来对我阿谀奉承
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由绮小姐的错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是由绮的错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从找到由绮  一切都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都变得不合拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:12:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不正好说明了由绮小姐存在的重要性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个习惯不会有什么好处的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从由绮小姐身上感受到了这么大的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是来嘲笑我的么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把画全部都看成一样的也不能怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉一切都是假的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不听长濑先生一再的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能一味地收购也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为您已经记不得在伦敦亲眼见过的那幅真品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然心里明白  但却不想承认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信拯救了自己的那幅画竟然被忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信这次的才是真品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜连理奈小姐都卖掉换来的那个也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也应该明白了  只是不去正视
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁这个好机会醒过来如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想理奈小姐的代价绝对不小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲子就不用了  我不是歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰奇  过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.37,0:13:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事情和你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那些讨人厌的画都赶紧处理掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我要住在这里  有工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不好呢  在夜里吃甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  白天抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来探病了？  听老爸说的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天跟理奈第一次出勤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我紧张得不得了  理奈她还是平时的理奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那么凛然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和玛瑙是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.94,0:13:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只见过一次  在由绮…森川由绮的演唱会上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:13:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  对了  还负责过森川由绮么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  也不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他  是由绮的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不太好吧  说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  没什么好隐瞒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我这随便乱猜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是因为这个才说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的日程安排呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次不一件件看也要记住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说…没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就去被藤井冬弥先生包下的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方理奈独唱演唱会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么…  真过分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事找学生处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才美咲和彰也在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去  虽然我想这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然彰他们也在的话就久违地大家一起去吃顿饭…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来还有个地方要去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和麻奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去和麻奈和好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没吵过架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上要考试了吧  我想总是把她带出来也不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是藤井…先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是山本  学生处的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么怎么样呢  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够呛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再给你介绍个其他的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  兼职的话现在有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:17:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心  我还在继续做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是给我介绍了一份好工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被叫做女神  鼓励了我  我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里我都不知道该怎么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么好事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是  呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意  我只是想道声谢而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很讨厌吧  和我这样的大妈一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从昨天开始了时间不规则的打工
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候都可以  因为很闲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的话倒是有空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天？  接下来？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太突然也不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  也不是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  去吗  接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想吃什么  我知道一家有好吃的法国料理的店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都好哪儿都好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为你陪我的谢礼  告诉你一件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  观月小姐的家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙  又…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个人不是学生处的职员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都可以…  只是在喝茶而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊  从以前起就对那家伙的性格…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是遥的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是理奈小姐吧  由绮的前辈的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能  绪方理奈和冬弥喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  和我的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就绝交
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不好哦  吃醋可不像彰君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像田丸一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道田丸君的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他变成那样的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他其实不是那么坏的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  美咲只是把他甩了而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  只是甩了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  好像变得消沉起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说观月小姐的妈妈是演艺事务所的社长就
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  为什么连名字都改了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要保密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对女儿周围的人啊  业界啊什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去…去一下厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为必须要打个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井先生才是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为已经吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的消遣的道具？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学的学生处的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已经不需要我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃醋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个词我可不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃醋了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要再和其他的女性一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所管不到的障碍物有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天森川由绮小姐就正式从流行歌曲工作室毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮今天不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有义务告诉他社员工演员的日程安排
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.50,0:24:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十一页
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.93,0:24:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要回到岔路口
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.66,0:24:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果选右边就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.99,0:24:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满了后悔的路程
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.59,0:24:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White  Album

